Subject: Shift4 Acquires Finaro

Team,
I am excited to announce that we finalized a deal to acquire Finaro, a cross-border
payments provider with a large European presence.
This acquisition underscores our aggressive efforts to deliver a unified commerce
experience across the world. This also enables our e-commerce capabilities to be
embedded globally for international merchants, as well as Shift4's restaurant and other
merchants that have a multi-national presence.
This is the first of two pending acquisitions we have underway and we look forward to
sharing details of the other soon.
You can read more in the press release below. As always, thank you for all of your
hard work and continued effort!
Jared
